<br>
The GUILDWARS of the Gods will be taking place only on the Firiona Vie Role Play Server. It is a running storyline that started between two guilds and their allies; the 1st Fist of Light and the Fist of Hate. They are nemesis guilds created for the intent of fighting one another in an evolving storyline through the use of creative guildwars that will have predefined rules and set conditions that will apply to them.<br>
<br>
Examples of such rules will be: <br>
<br>
Death rules, when your dead your dead and you do not re enter a fight. To help add to a sense of realism. This also includes no attacking dead people who are dragging corpses to a designated Graveyard (See Below).<br>
<br>
Rules of area engagement, I.E. fights will be set per area. If you flee the area you are out of the battle and cannot re enter the combat area until its resolved.<br>
<br>
Graveyards, where the dead can be drug to and looted so that they may then flee the combat area. When you loot and are dead in a Graveyard you must then flee the zone.<br>
<br>
These are just a few examples of some of the rules that may be implied during the course of an engagement. Of course you also may not know when there will be an engagement. After all, that trip to go save someone might end up with Guildwar being thrown in secret beforehand and you just never know what exactly is going to be happening.<br>
<br>
The entire scope of this evolving multi-guild server wide guildwar shall be engineered in a fashion similiar to that of a Dungeons and Dragons type game. The storyline will unfold based around character backgrounds and histories as they become relevant and exposed through the course of gameplay and interactions upon &quot;The GUILDWARS of the Gods&quot; forums located at www.1stfistoflight.com<br>
<br>
This will be a war that spans across the Firiona Vie server, with multiple battles, that all take place, nestled within the shadows of the Prophecy of Trakanon and the end times of Norrath. All those interested whom are interested and currently not in a guild or involved in an allied guild should &quot;sign up&quot; for &quot;enlistment&quot; at the forums under &quot;Recruiters Hall&quot; and specify which side you are interested in fighting for. Those guilds that wich to particpate and not allied yet should also post within the &quot;Recruiters Hall&quot; as well.<br>
<br>
The first battle which shall to tie into the storyline shall be &quot;The Battle for Takish-Hiz&quot;. A small sample of what is to come, and yes folks it is a guildwar fought INSIDE a dungeon. All events involved with the war as they transpire shall be maintained upon &quot;The Sages Scrolls&quot;, found upon the war forums. May the heavens shake with thunder, and ground tremble, for the fate of the world lies to the dogs of war. <p>Banegrivm Shadowblight<br>Sovereign Lord of the <a href=http://www.1stfistoflight.com>1st Fist of Light</a><br>Firiona Vie</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uartillis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Artillis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 207<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/20/02 12:40:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1155.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The GUILDWARS of the Gods</span><hr size=1> This sounds pretty cool.  May stop by for the fireworks <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uimogenelddar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ImogenElddar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/20/02 6:08:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1155.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The GUILDWARS of the Gods</span><hr size=1> I rather like 